snippet.title: Amber Hurley presents P3 Experience Business & Marketing Master Class featuring Tiana Von Johnson
snippet.description:
Amber Hurley Ent.  presents 

P3 Experience 
What’s your Perfect 3? 

Prayer Plan Preparation Purpose Passion 
Prosperity Prevail Power Perspective
Play Professional Profit Perseverance Progress Process 
Patience 

Featuring Tiana Von Johnson 
Business & Marketing Master Class 

Hosted & Music By: Tony Stover aka Bankroll Tony 

This event was for seasoned and inspiring entrepreneurs in any industry. It’s not the best business who wins it’s the best marketer that WINS! 

To book a consultation or more information email amberhurleyent@yahoo.com
